Steps to run Movie Cruiser App.

1. Clone the project using `git clone https://gitlab-cts.stackroute.in/Shubhendu.Mishra/moviecruiserserverapplication.git`
2. Navigate to `moviecruiserserverapplication/frontend` foler
3. Run `npm install`
4. Run `ng build --prod`
5. Navigate to `moviecruiserserverapplication/frontend/dist` folder and move contents of `moviecruiserfrontend` folder to its parent. Delete the empty folder.
6. Navigate to root folder and run `source ./build.sh`
7. Run `docker-compose up --build`

The application will be up and running at`http://localhost:4200`